ohh, ohh, ohh, ohh, ohh ♪"},{"s":12.3,"e":14.42,"text":"If mercy got a border..."},{"s":17.64,"e":21.56,"text":"...then mercy ain't complete."},{"s":24.08,"e":28.96,"text":"Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah."},{"s":29.96,"e":30.3,"text":"Whoo!"},{"s":33.12,"e":33.96,"text":"♪ Hey!"},{"s":36.84,"e":37.68,"text":"Ohh!"},{"s":39.98,"e":40.82,"text":"Yeah."},{"s":41.9,"e":42.74,"text":"Yeah."},{"s":42.74,"e":46.52,"text":"They heard about a beast down burning in the deep."},{"s":47.2,"e":49.92,"text":"Then turned the page and went back to sleep."},{"s":50.38,"e":51.7,"text":"Haunted in the smoke."},{"s":51.72,"e":53.38,"text":"Chained in the flame."},{"s":53.82,"e":56.76,"text":"Everybody pointing, nobody took blame."},{"s":56.76,"e":60.18,"text":"If one creature cries, then the whole world knows."},{"s":61.08,"e":63.48,"text":"What kind of garden lets that pain grow?"},{"s":63.76,"e":65.3,"text":"You can call him fallen."},{"s":65.72,"e":67.06,"text":"You can call him wrong."},{"s":67.38,"e":70.44,"text":"But leaving pain forever is a cruel old song."},{"s":70.52,"e":72.66,"text":"No creature left in fire."},{"s":73.94,"e":75.9,"text":"No soul beneath the stone."},{"s":77.22,"e":82.98,"text":"If love is getting higher, then nobody burns alone."},{"s":83.84,"e":86.34,"text":"The whole world heard the thunder."},{"s":87.54,"e":89.76,"text":"The whole world closed the door."},{"s":91.12,"e":93.18,"text":"No creature left in fire."},{"s":93.78,"e":97.44,"text":"Not one beast anymore."},{"s":99.4,"e":101.76,"text":"Justice without mercy turns cold in the hand."},{"s":102.34,"e":105,"text":"Rules without love don't heal the land."},{"s":105.5,"e":108.52,"text":"If heaven is holy and light is true,"},{"s":108.72,"e":111.66,"text":"then compassion got to reach the monster too."},{"s":111.66,"e":115.08,"text":"Not praising the darkness, not kissing the chain."},{"s":115.14,"e":118.52,"text":"Just saying forever pain is still pain."},{"s":118.6,"e":122.22,"text":"If we want peace, then we better get brave."},{"s":122.42,"e":126.48,"text":"Pull every lost thing out of the grave."},{"s":126.86,"e":127.52,"text":"Fear don't fix it."},{"s":127.56,"e":128.28,"text":"Fear don't heal."},{"s":128.4,"e":129.94,"text":"Love gets loud when the suffering's real."},{"s":129.98,"e":131.64,"text":"If one stays burning while the choir sing,"},{"s":131.72,"e":135.12,"text":"the mercy still ain't spread its wings."},{"s":135.58,"e":137.72,"text":"No creature left in fire."},{"s":139.08,"e":141.08,"text":"No soul beneath the stone."},{"s":142.04,"e":148.34,"text":"If love is getting higher, then nobody burns alone."},{"s":149.12,"e":151.46,"text":"The whole world heard the thunder."},{"s":152.6,"e":154.94,"text":"The whole world closed the door."},{"s":156.18,"e":158.3,"text":"No creature left in fire."},{"s":158.62,"e":160.52,"text":"Not one beast anymore."},{"s":164.02,"e":165.28,"text":"Drag the chains out."},{"s":165.64,"e":166.3,"text":"Cool the cold."},{"s":167.4,"e":169.8,"text":"Wash the smoke from every soul."},{"s":169.8,"e":171.7,"text":"No more cages."},{"s":171.84,"e":173.36,"text":"No more screams."},{"s":173.38,"e":175.44,"text":"No more nightmares."},{"s":176.2,"e":176.72,"text":"Sold as dreams."},{"s":188.2,"e":193.98,"text":"If mercy is real, it reaches the pit."},{"s":193.98,"e":202.48,"text":"If love is alive, it doesn't quit."}],"duration":211.27999877929688,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-05-22T02:29:50.532Z","model":"whisper-1"}